Karen Armstrong:

"The goal: Create a simple, concise, visually engaging website that invites and encourages people to learn, discuss, and share the merits of the Golden Rule with others. A few months later, we have a growing community of diverse people connecting on Facebook, Twitter, all sharing this timeless, universal message of peace, justice and compassion for all.

As this video and our experience shows, the Golden Rule is certainly an idea worth spreading. And unlike many ideas, this one has thousands of years of experimentation to back it up."




